veryone not to pay attention to a trivial issue.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1352}, {\"ngram\": \"the uniform\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1425}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1446}, {\"ngram\": \"a trivial issue\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1465}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Srettha also turned to his Facebook account on Wednesday to defend the Thai athletes' uniform for the Paris Olympics Games.\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1542, \"end\": 1546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\", \"score\": 0.5161968638259202, \"rank\": 0.757612483683512, \"text\": \"Thai\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mr Srettha\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1478}, {\"ngram\": \"his Facebook account\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics Games\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Patterns from the Ban Chiang World Historical Site inspired the design team.\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1615, \"end\": 1625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ban_Chiang\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ban Chiang\", \"types\": [\"Q9259\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ban_Chiang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ban_Chiang\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Patterns\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"the design team\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The outfit reflects the combination of Thai cultural heritage and internationalisation,\\\" he wrote.\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1713, \"end\": 1717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\", \"score\": 0.5161968638259202, \"rank\": 0.757612483683512, \"text\": \"Thai\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The outfit\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1684}, {\"ngram\": \"the combination\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1709}, {\"ngram\": \"internationalisation\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Srettha said the design team conducted thorough research by meeting Udon Thani Rajabhat University's Fabric and Textile Creative Design Centre (FTCDC) director.\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1845, \"end\": 1875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Udon_Thani_Rajabhat_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Udon Thani Rajabhat University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Udon_Thani_Rajabhat_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Udon_Thani_Rajabhat_University\"}, {\"begin\": 1878, \"end\": 1884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Textile\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0156820454558115e-26, \"text\": \"Fabric\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Textile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Textile\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mr Srettha\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1784}, {\"ngram\": \"the design team\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"thorough research\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said they gathered data and information and obtained advice from the Ban Chiang National Museum, the Fine Arts Department, and local communities that continue the tradition of weaving and the indigo dying process with the unique Ban Chiang patterns.\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 2190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2010, \"end\": 2020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ban_Chiang\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"